  "description": "Trefoil at high tangle (0.65) and 1.8 Hz pulse rate — the 3-crossing rotation manifests as a spinning sensation in the audio. Voices at moderate entrainment (0.4) feel like a mass rotating around a center. Triangle LFO maps tangle to feel like the rotation accelerating and slowing. Short decay keeps hits punchy.",
